  {
    | New       {}
    | Public    {}
    | Protected {}
    | Internal  {}
    | Private   {}
    | Virtual   {}
    | Volatile  {}
    | Static    {}
    | Readonly  {}
    | Sealed    {}
    | Override  {}
    | Abstract  {}
